42|49| God holds control over Heaven and Earth; He creates anything He wishes. He bestows a daughter on anyone He wishes and bestows a son on anyone He wishes; 
42|50| or marries them off, both male and female, and makes anyone He wishes barren. He is Aware, Capable. 
